{"type": "article", "id": 39561, "title": "Coach换新总裁，以及，连卡佛电商上线｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-04-07T03:21:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 33, "name": "上海"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 1029, "name": "Lego"}, {"id": 1038, "name": "Flyknit"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 6400, "name": "咖啡店"}, {"id": 9690, "name": "星战"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 20337, "name": "连卡佛"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170407100255gbzYUr4hjnMEHJ8T.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170406005311/en/Coach-Appoints-Joshua-Schulman-President-CEO-Coach\"><strong>Coach 任命新总裁</strong></a> | 从今年 6 月 5 日开始，Joshua Schulman 将担任 Coach 品牌的新总裁。他此前曾担任 Neiman Marcus 的总裁，Schulman 上任之后将主管 Coach 品牌的全球事宜，直接向 Coach 的集团总裁 Victor Luis 汇报工作。 </p><p><a href=\"http://www.linkshop.com.cn/web/archives/2017/374317.shtml?from=rss\"><strong>连卡佛集团旗下的华镫集团投资的电商平台正式上线</strong></a> | 这个电商平台叫 MyMM美美，名称来自华镫集团旗下的美美百货。第一批合作方包括 Lane Crawford、JOYCE Beauty、Rimowa、Furla、Tag Heuer、La Perla、Kate Spade 等品牌。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>最新发布的 2017 早秋系列中，<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/gucci-ace-sneaker-patches\">Gucci 带来了 Ace 系列小白鞋的更多玩法</a>。可拆卸、更换的球鞋配饰，丰富的色彩和元素的组合，其图案涵盖了 UFO、龙、豹子、凤梨、红唇、虎头与蝴蝶结等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105132amLiyCo4l3vu167V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105132XmYsH9PAzEJx36KF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105133VJzAfiB74E0Kx2he.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704071051336we0ZVWhoYRnAiXz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105133fxBj3ZP7HMesLSJG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105133zbCeYr2cAhFHI43G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105134LwilACcqV9GFBQsn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105132l7x0WtRfXvCG42cz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105145OJAuTm7ClVLGxvDj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105145n4TtYJfcvFwBbaSD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105146j7rUpdtInACXgm3N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105146zyskNi4H8BqSEIC6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/onitsuka-tiger-tiger-ally-denim-collection\">Onitsuka Tiger 推出全新丹宁系列 Tiger Ally 鞋款</a>。这款鞋的设计源自 80 年代慢跑鞋款 ALLIANCE，采用了日本的丹宁布料做鞋面，共有深蓝及白色两款，定价为 100 美元。现已于 Onitsuka Tiger 的官网发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105107c8ijBlMFR5zqwoAL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105107PmkTGL38lcd62xRe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105117rnNQDKW3jJHV9dlp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/puma-sneaker-cafe-blackbird-shanghai\">4 月 7 日至 5 月 7 日期间，PUMA 联合位于上海乌鲁木齐南路的餐厅 BLACKBIRDS 开设限定咖啡 SNEAKER CAFE</a>。活动期间，BLACKBIRDS 特别开辟了一隅历史墙，回顾 PUMA 品牌的经典时刻及包括 Creeper、Suede、Disc Blaze 和 Trinomic 在内的不同时代知名鞋款。另外还有为 PUMA 特制的餐食，包括两款从 PUMA Sneaker 中汲取灵感的下午茶 ——B.O.G In The Box 套餐和 Basket Heart In The Box 套餐。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105030jhBivK90eUzkmnb2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105024Q0x96OTPi1pASZlU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105026YvUTP41EL2FRXhIg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105030EkdobpC7BuGwnelZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105048nfq3TvBPeYlcaozU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105028he8Bxl370cyFnLIg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105029A7n6yHWw2v5XjJdV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105030RGV0uPWDiOrAQEYb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105030K5sPZNH9RaEehbLO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105047rX7wHUkB5WuoqAY6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407105047RWwIiplhOorbmPaM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704071050477SngFO2rmwtCuR0p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>为庆祝《Star Wars: Episode IV – A New Hope》的 40 周年，<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/lego-star-wars-detention-block-rescue-for-star-wars-celebration\">LEGO 将推出 Star Wars Celebration 会场限定版积木模型</a>，将当中 Han Solo 与 Luke Skywalker 打扮成白兵到潜入死星的拘留室 AA-23 营救 Princess Leia 场景重现。这款模型极难入手，需要在 Star Wars Celebration 会场登记抽签，才有可能买到。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704071050116rWhI87JxGw0o3Mt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>我们前几天报道过的 Acne Studios 的牛仔支线唯一专卖店 <a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/407377\">Acne Studios Blå Konst</a>，昨日于东京涩谷正式开幕。这里有更多的图：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104717plQbwZve9xsCJNmo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104725OW2xAwHeUVLhdR95.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104732qMFab4r6BPZ2dm9G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104732uIoBT0HeLyz6ASV4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104732TKYEpJihr7XsaGIZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104732rLDVMKFYzBxjt8il.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104741Ar8N0PYpVsFlndM9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017040710474987SI3jBPd2Q5uxLE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>据说这可能是今夏最热门的鞋款：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/nikelab-air-sock-racer-flyknit\">经典的袜式鞋 Nike Air Sock Racer，发布全新 Flyknit 改良版本</a>，以及全新的三款配色。该系列均采用 Flyknit 针织材质袜式鞋身，鞋头处以醒目的对比色 Swoosh 作点缀，搭载轻盈柔韧的 Nike Free 跑步大底。目前已于 <a href=\"https://kith.com/collections/nike/mens\">KITH</a> 发售，每双定价为 140 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104850I8tgl03zd5aqjePk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667241\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104950F0aqk54Xr9sVBiMo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667728\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104950x982AXEzuvStqiOg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667728\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104951OhmVPkGji6Nduavg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104951aCyqUsAfQdv4mhiB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667728\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104950D3Icqa5ymJgoZY28.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170407104951Ketn1N3vDVwTbOYj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/4/puma-sneaker-cafe-blackbird-shanghai\">hypebeast</a></p>"}